<italic>Note</italic>: OPC, Psychiatric Outpatient Clinic; CSPSB, Clinician-supported Problem-solving Based Bibliotherapy; UOFS, Usual outpatient family support; ECI, Experience of Caregiving Inventory; FBIS, Family Burden Interview Schedule; SPSI-R:S, Social Problem-Solving Inventory-Revised: Short version; PANSS, Positive and Negative Syndrome Scale; SLOF, Specific Level of Functioning Scale. Time 1 = baseline measurement at recruitment; Time 2 = 1 week after completion of intervention; Time 3 = 6 months after completion of intervention; Time 4 = 12 months after completion of intervention.</p></fn><fn id="fn-07" fn-type="other"><p>
<sup>a</sup>For ECI, the higher the mean score the more negative the appraisal of family carers to their caregiving experiences.</p></fn><fn id="fn-08" fn-type="other"><p>
